title: Fatal error: Could not get class storage for callable class in Twig_Function constructor
body:
Psalm 3.6.6@5e17a9af104de39321c47f73b253cece9df1cf2c
twig/twig 2.6.2@7d7342c8a4059fefb9b8d07db0cc14007021f9b7

Code to reproduce (it doesn't matter whether `Foo::bar` exists).
```
<?php

class MyTwigExtension extends \Twig_Extension {

    public function getFunctions(): array {
        return [
            new \Twig_Function(
                'bar',
                ['\Foo', 'bar']
            ),
        ];
    }
}
```
